<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
  <title>About Us</title>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <nav class="navbar">
    
        <div class="container">
            
            <a href="#" class="navbar-brand">About Us</a>
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
                </li>
                {{#if user}}
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/profile" class="nav-link">Profile</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/reserv" class="nav-link">Reservation</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/settings" class="nav-link">Settings</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/auth/logout" class="nav-link">Log Out</a>
                </li>
                {{else}}
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/login" class="nav-link">Log In</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/register" class="nav-link">Register</a>
                </li>
                {{/if}}
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/register" class="nav-link">Register</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/about-us" class="nav-link">About Us</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <h1>About The Delicious Bistro</h1>
  </header>

  

  <main>
    <section id="overview">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        <img src="https://foaps.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/How-To-Effectively-Choose-Your-Restaurant-Location.jpg" alt="location">
        The Delicious Bistro is a renowned restaurant that has been serving delightful meals to our customers for over a decade.
        We take pride in providing a warm and inviting atmosphere along with a menu that caters to diverse tastes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="mission">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        <img src="https://blogassets.7shifts.com/2021/09/restaurant-mission-statement--1-.jpg" alt="mission">
        Our mission is to create an exceptional dining experience for our guests by offering delicious, high-quality food prepared with passion and served with a smile.
        We strive to exceed expectations and become the go-to destination for those seeking a memorable culinary journey.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="team">
      <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
      <p>
        <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/56a2785c69a91af45e06a188/1581365843264-DO7TUXG42RM2436XIX6K/Restaurant-Future-Leadership.png?format=1500w" alt="restaurants team in one picture ">
        Behind every great dish is a talented team of chefs and staff. At The Delicious Bistro, our team is dedicated to crafting culinary masterpieces that leave a lasting impression.
        Get to know the faces behind the scenes who work tirelessly to bring you the best dining experience.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <h2>Contact us:</h2>
  <form action="#" method="post">
    <label for="name">Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
  
    <label for="email">Email:</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
  
    <label for="message">Message:</label>
    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
  
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
  </form>
  

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2022 The Delicious Bistro</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
